{"tid":1499383,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"核彈級文宣！香港英文版以科學分析還原811紀錄片、實驗片同長達25頁英文Interim report緊急發放！","createTime":"2019-08-23T16:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T02:47:10.000Z","uid":1806,"like":186,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"79cac61a4d1c60e10fab210e9499ba6c2836b75e","tid":1499383,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">文宣爆Seed！科學揭開真相，香港首套以科學分析還原811紀錄片誕生，並會製作英文版流出國際<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/afajJbU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/afajJbU</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>英文版&lt;&lt;The Investigation: Ep.01 - 811事件&gt;&gt;上線啦</strong></span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IFICuOtpdx0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIFICuOtpdx0&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6hPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=1511425f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IFICuOtpdx0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地都同步先趕急發放<strong>英文版 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Interim Report</span></strong> 解釋返大家既疑問 eg. 點解我地會咁推斷既？我地係點樣去計返黎？用咩theory？點樣去推測大概位置？等等大家都可以一目了然。</span></span></strong><br />\nDownload Link: <a href=\"http://cdn.hkgetv.com/project/the-investigation/811/An_Investigation_on_the_Incident.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hkgetv.com%2Fproject%2Fthe-investigation%2F811%2FAn_Investigation_on_the_Incident.pdf&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6hPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=aa5b280a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.hkgetv.com/project/the-investigation/811/An_Investigation_on_the_Incident.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sv1ax2G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSv1ax2G.png&h=b18f2486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地希望依份報告可以解答到各位既疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">實驗片</span></span></strong><strong>：在超近距離使用丫叉發射彈珠在3M護目鏡的效果</strong><br />\n感謝外國手足協助拍攝同完成一個簡單實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以睇到係咁近距離之下，3M護目鏡只留有痕跡<br />\n唔會發生破裂。<br />\n所以可以諗下受傷既女仔係環境證據同依一條實驗片下<br />\n女仔受咩所傷，答案呼之欲出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J1xX2vypGgE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ1xX2vypGgE&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6hPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=f1c23e5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J1xX2vypGgE</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>再次重申：我地將運用一切所知既科學知識還原事件真相，並用科學去分析多段新聞直播片段、環境證據、重組時間線，嘗試發掘事件任何既新發現，把真相呈現大家眼前，破解各種流言蜚語。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>影片將分為7個部分<br />\n<blockquote>1. 維園及深水埗和平集會<br />\n2. 示威者走出馬路設置路障<br />\n3. 警民爆發衝突警方發射催淚彈<br />\n4. 九龍區快閃行動以及灣仔防暴推進&lt;雙線&gt;<br />\n5. 尖沙咀警察濫暴濫權<br />\n6. 葵芳站施放催淚彈現場一片混亂<br />\n7. 荃灣、北角打成一片警方混示威人群</strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望能助大眾知道事件真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">以理服人，請幫我地一齊推上國際。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n各位支持我地既巴絲，我地會上載埋fb同ig，大家可以去埋fb／ig幫手Share 我地既片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">除左Facebook Page, YouTube Channel 同 Instagram (包括IGTV) 作文宣渠道，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地開左Twitter啦</span></span>。<br />\n<blockquote>YouTube Channel: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w%2Ffeatured&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6hPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=09ea4179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured</a><br />\nOur Facebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKGETV%2F&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6hPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=d5257eca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/</a><br />\nOur Instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKGETV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKGETV%2F&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6hPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=da7037ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/HKGETV/</a><br />\nOur Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkgetv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkgetv&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6hPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=f491e284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkgetv</a></blockquote></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b6fa4f78ffc9349ed0bd4cec13c8fc57ef445d1f","tid":1499383,"uid":213977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba8269ae0f91c3fa38ece63e026b16a1a02823c","tid":1499383,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1712aa64f011e1e45e40882bbebe05ce0c73a223","tid":1499383,"uid":135554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:39:58.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"5a50f2b3db2783371b89395f094db8407cdc9bb5","tid":1499383,"uid":74452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:40:55.000Z","msg":"824觀塘"}